Template: ossec-hids-server/emailto
Type: string
Default: root@localhost
_Description: The email to send alerts to
 This is the general email where alerts will be sent to.
 For finer grain, you can add other specific rules inside the ossec.conf file

Template: ossec-hids-server/emailfrom
Type: string
Default: ossecm@ossec.server
_Description: The email origin from
 This is the email adress where alerts will come from.

Template: ossec-hids-server/smtpserver
Type: string
Default: localhost
_Description: smtp server address (name or ip)

